plot: The Doctor, Bill and Nardole discover a tomb of the Queen of the Ice Warriors on Mars in 1881.

The Doctor, Bill, and Nardole arrive on Mars on the year 1881 by some cryptic messages uncovered by NASA; where they discover Victorian soldiers were brought there and now are colonizing the red planet for the glory of the British Empire. But suddenly they find the tomb of the queen of an alien race known as the Ice Warriors, that are native of Mars. When the queen is awoken from her cryogenic sleep, the TARDIS team is caught in the middle of a war between Humans and Ice Warriors, but as the humans are now the invaders this time around, in which side will The Doctor stand?—Jose Benavides
